{
  "stem": "2391.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they said-- so the-- and they were soldiers, British and French soldiers defending this train station, which supposedly was the last, their last fort or whatever where they--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they broke-- I remember, with their rifles-- they broke the windows all around, and then standing behind those windows and shooting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the shooting started like crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they came with some sandbags.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they felt, you know, they had to do something for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The came with sandbags and said, here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put sandbags up for protection for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were hiding in this little corner there, surrounded by sandbags.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember there was this one-- some of-- some of the people-- it is interesting, when you're in a situation like this and you think this is the end, how people react differently.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some people stay very calm, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, OK, so I'm going to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Big deal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some people, they go completely crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They, they have these, these nervous breakdowns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was this guy, he was screaming and crying and, ah, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "God save me and all that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was looking at this guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, this guy it crazy, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- it didn't bother me that much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I learned to-- and I did that later too-- to detach myself in a way from reality, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just like looking at myself from, from, from a distance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Hey, what are you doing here, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I thought, I'm going to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's no big deal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This sort of attitude.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's the only thing that can-- that helps you survive in a horrible situation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not everybody has this ability.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard other people say that too.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
